{{version030}}

{{flavour|Throws a bolt of electricity at the target, with high accuracy.}}

'''Electrical Bolt''' is a monster-only spell that is similar to [[Lightning Bolt]]. Electrical bolts can pierce through enemies and bounce from walls, potentially causing a [[doublezap]]. As BEAM_ELEC damage, it ignores 1/2 of your [[AC]]. Compared to Lightning Bolt, this spell is more accurate, has more dice, and doesn't create nearly as loud of a [[noise]].

